org.neo4j.helpers

Annotation Type Service.Implementation


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=SOURCE)
public static @interface Service.Implementation
    Designates that a class implements the specified service and should be added to the services listings file (META-INF/services/[service-name]).

    The annotation in itself does not provide any functionality for adding the implementation class to the services listings file. But it serves as a handle for an Annotation Processing Tool to utilize for performing that task.

    Author:
    Tobias Ivarsson
